---
title: Coconut Dal with Spinach and Warm Naan Bread
description: This coconut lentil dal is delicious! Fluffy naan bread is the perfect tool to scoop up this coconut-ty goodness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/coconut-dal-e57669a1.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/dal-a-la-noix-de-coco-5c8ac4acc445fa2cd1019802-a0fb5798.pdf
